        {
            "id": 6287579,
            "title": "盤中速報 - 榮科(4989)大漲7.07%，報45.45元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>榮科(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:4989:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/4989\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">4989-TW</a>)24日13:13股價上漲3元，報45.45元，漲幅7.07%，成交24,528張。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>榮科(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:4989:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/4989\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">4989-TW</a>)所屬產業為電子零組件業，主要業務為電解銅箔之製造及銷售。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>近5日股價上漲4.43%，集中市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>上漲2.81%，股價漲幅表現優於大盤。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：+106 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：+107 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：0 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：-1 張</li> <li>融資增減：+142 張</li> <li>融券增減：-3,607 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
            "link": "https://news.cnyes.com/news/id/6287579",
